list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment: Fixed bugs and one step closer to the final release

task.summary:
Mandi Admin Module is ready (made both the frontend and the backend).
Union Admin's backend is complete.
TruckOwner's module is 70% complete. A user can accept a bid from live routes list now from a proper functioning frontend.
Live Auction List is working nicely now. Trucks live status list is also working. Only dashboard data and adding, removing trucks is remaining from truck owner's module.

Changed the business logic for updating routes for each truck item after closing bid. Also moved the live truck data from google firebase to google firestore as some complex queries were needed on the data. Now all of the cloud data is provided by google firebase cloud storage and google firestore.
Code optimizations and added "Active" property to truck class.
Fixed truck owner dashboard timer bug...it took a whole day but finally it is solved.
Fixed the broken history list for pahunch admin, now working nicely.
Fully completed pahunch admin module. I'm feeling happy today:)
